                <head>No. 392.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Morgan</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Frelinghuysen</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Mexico</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1883-04-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">April</hi> 21, 1883</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Morgan cables that he is informed by telegraph from our consul at Mazatlan
                    that Captain Caleb is sentenced to five years’ imprisonment, that the Adriana is
                    confiscated and the crew released, and that the case has been appealed.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
